vue 双向绑定大致原理
function defineReactive(obj, key, value) {
  var dep = new Dep()
  Object.defineProperty(obj, key, {
    enumerable: true,
    configurable: true,
    get: function reactiveGetter() {
      if (Dep.target) {
        dep.depend()
      }
      return value
    },
    set: function reactiveSetter(newVal) {
      if (value === newVal) {
        return
      } else {
        value = newVal
        dep.notify()
      }
    }
  })
}
